election_record.label: New York 1805 Assembly, Dutchess County

overview.note: Joseph Belding, Lewis Dibble, John D. Ostrom, Benjamin Hasbrouck, and Shelden Monger were listed on the "Seceders Ticket," according to newspaper sources. Joseph C. Fields and John Van Benthuysen were also supported by this ticket.
Benjamin Carver is an amalgamation of two candidates.
